Note:
1. EH or EL edge at level 2 target to terminal
2. nonX reduction rules will only be applied to terminal encoding with boolean range
3. identify reduction rule in the BDDs where it is not allowed
4. build legal edge: long edge should be built if it is illegal
5. unreduce edge: when push-down reduced edge in mergeEdge
